{"tid":1790001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東涌逸東邨上月刑毀案兩少年被捕","createTime":"2019-12-19T16:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:28:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9907df9c805164c7e2deddf27a0720bce36dbbba","tid":1790001,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕兩名少年, 涉嫌與東涌發生的刑事毀壞案有關.<br />\n        事發在上月19號上午六時許, 逸東街八號一間食肆及一間店鋪, 被四名男子毀壞. 大嶼山警區反三合會行動組人員經深入調查後, 今日在逸東邨一個單位內, 拘捕兩名分別13和14歲的少年, 兩人涉嫌刑事毀壞, 現已獲准保釋候查, 下月中向警方報到. 警方說, 不排除有更多人被捕.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20191219225535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191219225535&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5a3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=9e260206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20191219225535</a>"},{"pid":"6005065d67348827f6cb7434a99e5445e9c6623b","tid":1790001,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"警方說, 不排除有更多人被捕."},{"pid":"9d7deab4c9593108999ea3934f70305e0a1d9bce","tid":1790001,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d8771f2dca9d10fd1cfb53c74fa3587e56ddbd","tid":1790001,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce66ddc10c640870ba46b30ee0338fb141f473be","tid":1790001,"uid":70147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im